{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2681 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2681 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Compiler Error C2681","pos":[597,617]},{"content":"'type' : invalid expression type for name","pos":[618,659]},{"content":"A casting operator tried to convert from an invalid type.","pos":[666,723]},{"content":"For example, if you use the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>dynamic_cast<ept id=\"p1\">](../../cpp/dynamic-cast-operator.md)</ept> operator to convert an expression to a pointer type, the source expression must be a pointer.","pos":[724,896],"source":" For example, if you use the [dynamic_cast](../../cpp/dynamic-cast-operator.md) operator to convert an expression to a pointer type, the source expression must be a pointer."},{"content":"The following sample generates C2681:","pos":[903,940]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2681 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2681\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2681\"\nms.assetid: eb42da6d-8d2c-43fd-986b-e73e2b004885\ncaps.latest.revision: 7\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2681\n'type' : invalid expression type for name  \n  \n A casting operator tried to convert from an invalid type. For example, if you use the [dynamic_cast](../../cpp/dynamic-cast-operator.md) operator to convert an expression to a pointer type, the source expression must be a pointer.  \n  \n The following sample generates C2681:  \n  \n```  \n// C2681.cpp  \nclass A { virtual void f(); };  \n  \nvoid g(int i) {  \n    A* pa;  \n    pa = dynamic_cast<A*>(i);  // C2681  \n}  \n```"}